    <title><custom ref="errores-cool-titulo"/></title>
    <p>
      [++++++++++++++++++]
    </p>
    <p>Students show they understand which categories to compare, but they use numbers that are not based on the scale of the graph.</p>
  </paragraphs>


  <!-- Estrategia de apoyo si muchos estudiantes respondieron incorrectamente -->
